OL,3,C'Would be better' if Tory MPs selected
OL,4,Cleader, says Lord Hague
OL,6,FFormer Conservative leader Lord Hague
OL,7,Fhas said that it "would be better" if
OL,8,Fthe party's leadership was decided by
OL,9,FMPs, rather than the membership.
OL,11,FTory members are preparing to select a
OL,12,Fnew leader after Rishi Sunak announced
OL,13,Fhe was standing down following the
OL,14,Fparty's general election defeat in the
OL,15,Fsummer.
