OL,3,C'Would be better' if Tory MPs selected
OL,4,Cleader, says Lord Hague
OL,6,FAsked about the membership making the
OL,7,Ffinal decision on who will be party
OL,8,Fleader, Lord Hague told the Radio 4
OL,9,Fprogramme: "That's my fault, I
OL,10,Fintroduced these rules.
OL,12,F"But now we can see the world has
OL,13,Fchanged, political parties are smaller.
OL,15,F"It would be better if the decision
OL,16,Fwas in the hands of Members of
OL,17,FParliament because the party
OL,18,Fmembership has become so small."
