OL,3,C'Would be better' if Tory MPs selected
OL,4,Cleader, says Lord Hague
OL,6,FHowever, he said that MPs "still play
OL,7,Fa very big role" so "they have to be
OL,8,Fvery careful who they support in case
OL,9,Fthey give the impression to the
OL,10,Fmembers that they're happy with
OL,11,Fsomeone they're not really happy with".
OL,13,FThe race for the Tory leadership will
OL,14,Ffeature prominently in the party's
OL,15,Fconference.
OL,17,FThe four candidates will be lobbying
OL,18,FMPs before parliamentarians pick the
OL,19,Ffinal two on October 10. Members will
OL,20,Fchoose between those two, with the
OL,21,Fresult declared on November 2.
